msgid "Save Settings"
msgstr "儲存設定"

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid ""
"These settings control how your custom pages are displayed in the Fluent "
"Community sidebar menu."
msgstr "這些設定控制您的自訂頁面在 Fluent Community 側邊欄選單中的顯示方式。"

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid "No custom pages found. Create some pages first."
msgstr "找不到自訂頁面。請先建立一些頁面。"

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid "Select which pages to include in the menu:"
msgstr "選擇要包含在選單中的頁面："

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid "Select All"
msgstr "全選"

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid "Leave all unchecked to include all pages."
msgstr "全部取消勾選以包含所有頁面。"

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid ""
"Drag and drop to reorder pages in the menu. This order overrides the default "
"ordering."
msgstr "拖放即可重新排列選單中的頁面順序。此順序將覆蓋預設順序。"

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid "Drag and drop pages to set their order in the menu."
msgstr "拖放頁面即可設定其在選單中的順序。"

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid "Configure how custom pages appear in the Fluent Community menu."
msgstr "設定自訂頁面在 Fluent Community 選單中的顯示方式。"

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid "Menu Options"
msgstr "選單選項"

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid "Show custom pages in the Fluent Community sidebar menu"
msgstr "在 Fluent Community 側邊欄選單中顯示自訂頁面"

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid "Menu Icon"
msgstr "選單圖示"

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid "Use emoji or leave blank. Examples: 📄 📑 📋 📃 📜"
msgstr "請使用表情符號或留空。例如：📄 📑 📋 📃 📜"

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid "Include \"Page Settings\" link in the menu group"
msgstr "在選單組中新增“頁面設定”連結"

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid "Lower numbers appear higher in the menu (default: 50)"
msgstr "選單中數字越小，顯示位置越前（預設值：50）"

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid ""
"Drag and drop to reorder pages in the menu. This order overrides the default "
"order."
msgstr "拖放即可重新排列選單中的頁面順序。此順序將覆蓋預設順序。"

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid "About FCA Pages"
msgstr "關於FCA頁面"

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid ""
"FCA Pages allows you to create and manage custom pages inside your Fluent "
"Community portal."
msgstr "FCA Pages 可讓您在 Fluent Community 入口網站內建立和管理自訂頁面。"

#: includes/class-fca-settings.php
msgid "Settings are stored securely and persist between page refreshes."
msgstr "設定資訊安全儲存，頁面刷新後依然有效。"

